  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Banner of Conquest\" is a Three Kingdoms-themed Survivor-like (Bullet Heaven) game.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here, historical legends transform into <strong>OP stat monsters</strong>. Your goal is simple: Survive the wave, get rich, and become unstoppably strong!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/15c3989c762b9f0f8d7d14ac7f256d59.poster.avif?t=1764647961\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/15c3989c762b9f0f8d7d14ac7f256d59.webm?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/15c3989c762b9f0f8d7d14ac7f256d59.mp4?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/02d0879ddebd5a4594ba0008c3a704e9.avif?t=1764647961\" width=600 height=140 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Break the Game with 20+ Unique Heroes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Zhao Yun, Lu Bu, Guan Yu, and more. Each character brings a unique, rule-breaking mechanic to the table.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to experience a Broken Build? Choose Emperor Xian. His unique trait allowing you to grab everything in the shop for <strong>ZERO GOLD</strong>. Experience the joy of scaling your stats to infinity for free!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/9afe98eb958645061430cf8c040bdfb2.poster.avif?t=1764647961\" width=802 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/9afe98eb958645061430cf8c040bdfb2.webm?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/9afe98eb958645061430cf8c040bdfb2.mp4?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Evolve from Scrap Iron to legendary weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine dozens of weapons with 100+ Stratagem Cards to create your own combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A special weapon crafting system allows even simple blades to be upgraded into legendary weapons with immense power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/9cc1e913a20f2a25cd006c0c5724e5e9.poster.avif?t=1764647961\" width=802 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/9cc1e913a20f2a25cd006c0c5724e5e9.webm?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/9cc1e913a20f2a25cd006c0c5724e5e9.mp4?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shop, Build, Survive (Brotato Style)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mindless killing isn't enough; you need a strategy. The game features a classic Wave + Shop cycle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between enemy waves, use your gold wisely. Reroll the shop to find that one specific Stratagem Card or Weapon to complete your build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine Mounts, Stratagems, and Hero Traits to craft your ultimate build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/16a0f4b272723f8120808fb0b48057d8.poster.avif?t=1764647961\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/16a0f4b272723f8120808fb0b48057d8.webm?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/16a0f4b272723f8120808fb0b48057d8.mp4?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step onto the battlefield, slay the generals, and conquer the chaos!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"Banner of Conquest\" is a Three Kingdoms-themed Survivor-like (Bullet Heaven) game.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Here, historical legends transform into <strong>OP stat monsters</strong>. Your goal is simple: Survive the wave, get rich, and become unstoppably strong!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/15c3989c762b9f0f8d7d14ac7f256d59.poster.avif?t=1764647961\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/15c3989c762b9f0f8d7d14ac7f256d59.webm?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/15c3989c762b9f0f8d7d14ac7f256d59.mp4?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/02d0879ddebd5a4594ba0008c3a704e9.avif?t=1764647961\" width=600 height=140 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Break the Game with 20+ Unique Heroes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play as Zhao Yun, Lu Bu, Guan Yu, and more. Each character brings a unique, rule-breaking mechanic to the table.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Want to experience a Broken Build? Choose Emperor Xian. His unique trait allowing you to grab everything in the shop for <strong>ZERO GOLD</strong>. Experience the joy of scaling your stats to infinity for free!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/9afe98eb958645061430cf8c040bdfb2.poster.avif?t=1764647961\" width=802 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/9afe98eb958645061430cf8c040bdfb2.webm?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/9afe98eb958645061430cf8c040bdfb2.mp4?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Evolve from Scrap Iron to legendary weapons</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine dozens of weapons with 100+ Stratagem Cards to create your own combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A special weapon crafting system allows even simple blades to be upgraded into legendary weapons with immense power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/9cc1e913a20f2a25cd006c0c5724e5e9.poster.avif?t=1764647961\" width=802 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/9cc1e913a20f2a25cd006c0c5724e5e9.webm?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/9cc1e913a20f2a25cd006c0c5724e5e9.mp4?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Shop, Build, Survive (Brotato Style)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mindless killing isn't enough; you need a strategy. The game features a classic Wave + Shop cycle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Between enemy waves, use your gold wisely. Reroll the shop to find that one specific Stratagem Card or Weapon to complete your build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combine Mounts, Stratagems, and Hero Traits to craft your ultimate build.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/16a0f4b272723f8120808fb0b48057d8.poster.avif?t=1764647961\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/16a0f4b272723f8120808fb0b48057d8.webm?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2483730/extras/16a0f4b272723f8120808fb0b48057d8.mp4?t=1764647961\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step onto the battlefield, slay the generals, and conquer the chaos!</p>",
